  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Architectural Drafter",
  "description": "<p>Responsibilities</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Able to co-ordinate and execute the operational work schedules and implementation of the Architectural work trade on site with sub-contractors, clients and Consultants to achieve target set.</li>\n  <li>Liaise with the sub-contractors to ensure smooth progression and timely completion of quality works in accordance to schedule and all required regulations</li>\n  <li>Site coordination and monitoring architectural work progress</li>\n  <li>Able to prepare shop drawing for construction &amp; As-built plan for submission</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Possess recognized Nitec in Building (Architectural) / Diploma in Architecture from local polytechnic or recognized institution.</li>\n  <li>Minimum 5 years’ experience in construction industry.</li>\n  <li>Able to work under pressure in a fast-paced environment.</li>\n  <li>Initiative, willingness to learn and able to multi-task.</li>\n  <li>Performs related responsibilities as required or assigned.</li>\n  <li>Able to work independently, capability to do trouble-shooting</li>\n  <li>Able to start work in short notice.</li>\n  <li>Ensure quality of works is achieved and safety regulations are complied with</li>\n</ul>",
